				Road construction company «AVTOBAN» JSC
			</p>

			<p>
				RCC "AVTOBAN" JSC is one of the five largest Russian road construction companies, the total portfolio of orders, including contracts in the form of PPP, is more than 180 billion rubles.
			</p>

			<p>
				RCC "AVTOBAN" JSC performs:
			</p>

			<ul>
